This topic describes how to upgrade <%= vars.product_full %> (<%= vars.product_abbr %>).

##<a id="assume"></a>Prerequisites

Verify that you have the correct component versions for the version of <%= vars.product_abbr %> that
you are upgrading to. See the [Features Snapshot](./index.html#snapshot)
or the download page on [Pivotal Network](https://network.pivotal.io/products/p-fim-addon/).

##<a id="upgrade"></a>Upgrade <%= vars.product_abbr %>

To upgrade <%= vars.product_abbr %> from 1.x to 2.x:

1. SSH into the <%= vars.ops_manager %> VM.
   For how to do this, see [SSH into <%= vars.ops_manager %>](https://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/customizing/trouble-advanced.html#ssh).

1. To delete the existing runtime configs, run the following command(s):

    ```
    bosh -e BOSH-ENVIRONMENT delete-config --type=runtime --name=fim
    bosh -e BOSH-ENVIRONMENT delete-config --type=runtime --name=fim-windows
    ```

1. To install the 2.x tile, follow the installation instructions in [Install <%= vars.product_abbr %>](./installing.html#install-addon).
